### Readings and Learning Resources Completed

‚Ä¢ Buelta (2022) on secure architecture patterns and modular design  
‚Ä¢ Velepucha and Flores (2023) on microservices principles and design challenges  
‚Ä¢ ISO/IEC 27000 Section 3 terminology related to access control and accountability  
‚Ä¢ OWASP Top 10 2021 risk awareness  
‚Ä¢ Lecturecast content introducing UML and security design modelling

These readings helped form a deeper understanding of how authentication, authorisation, input validation, and service boundaries should be enforced at the design stage.

